addLockPeriod(uint256).details: Only callable by the contract owner.

params.newLockPeriod: The new lock period in seconds.

params.period: The lock period to add rewards to
params.rewardAmount: The amount of rewards to add

deposit(uint256,uint256,uint256,bytes).details: Allows a user to deposit tokens, which are supplied to the AccessManagedMSV. Position is tracked by a unique depositId.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to deposit
params.deadline: The deadline for the permit signature
params.period: The lock period chosen for this deposit
params.signature: The permit signature for token approval

returns.sharesToMint: The number of shares minted for this deposit

initialize(address,address,uint256[]).details: Sets up the contract owner, pausable state, and approves the liquidity manager to spend tokens.

params._accessManagedMSV: The address of the AccessManagedMSV contract.
params._lockPeriods: Array of supported lock periods in seconds.
params._token: The address of the ERC20 token to be deposited.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

pause().details: Only callable by the contract owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unpause().details: Only callable by the contract owner.

params.newFee: The new fee in basis points (0-10000)

withdraw(bytes32).details: Only the position owner can withdraw. Handles early withdrawal fees and reward distribution.

params.depositId: The ID of the position to withdraw from

returns.amountToTransfer: The amount of token transferred to the user

addLockPeriod(uint256).notice: Add a new lock period to the supported list.

addRewards(uint256,uint256).notice: Add rewards to the reward pool (owner only)

deposit(uint256,uint256,uint256,bytes).notice: Open a new position in the pool

initialize(address,address,uint256[]).notice: Initializes the contract with the token, liquidity manager, and supported lock periods.

pause().notice: Pauses the contract, disabling deposits and withdrawals.

unpause().notice: Unpauses the contract, enabling deposits and withdrawals.

updateEarlyWithdrawalFee(uint256).notice: Update the early withdrawal fee (owner only)

withdrawProtocolFees().notice: Withdraw protocol fees to the contract owner
